## 🏗️ 3. ALLOCATION STRUCTURES (REAL-WORLD VIEW)

### 🧩 Intuition
“Where does this actually run?”

### 📘 Definition
Allocation maps software elements → hardware / runtime environment

### 🔥 Keras Allocation

| Software Part          | Runs Where                  |
|------------------------|-----------------------------|
| Model / Layer          | Python                      |
| Ops / Backend (TF/JAX) | Computation engine          |
| Numerical ops          | CPU / GPU                   |

**🧱 Diagram**

```mermaid
graph TD
    Python["Python (Model / Layer)"]
    Backend["Backend (TF / JAX Ops)"]
    GPU["GPU / CPU"]

    Python --> Backend
    Backend --> GPU
```

### ⚡ Why Allocation Matters

- **Performance**  
  CPU → slower  
  GPU → faster (orders of magnitude)

- **Scalability**  
  Good allocation → scalable system  
  Poor allocation → bottlenecks

**🔥 Key Insight**  
- Python **orchestrates**  
- Backend **executes**  
- GPU/CPU **computes**

